    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban boilers that use natural gas in all new house builds",
        "additional_details": "To mitigate catastrophic damage to the environment through burning fossil fuels, we want the Government to disallow installation of gas boilers in new builds for human habitation effective immediately.",
        "background": "A 2021 study suggests that the UK\u2019s home gas boilers emit twice as much CO\u2082 as all UK power stations.",
